# Block all contents of this directory by default. Per-session subagent
# research artifacts live here transient — they should NOT auto-commit
# alongside spec docs.
#
# Promoting a specific artifact to durable preservation = move it to
# orgs/ascendops/docs/durable/ as a separate per-artifact decision.
# That path is covered by the !orgs/<org>/docs/durable/** carve-out
# in the top-level .gitignore.
#
# This file itself is tracked so the directory exists in the repo and
# the convention path resolves for receivers following the
# contract-at-dispatch v2 RESEARCH_ARTIFACT_PATH sub-bullet.
*
!.gitignore
